---
title: Tex-Mex Beef Bake & Cheesy Potatoes with Yoghurt & Chives
description: This family winner combines mild Mexican spices with tender beef and veggies. The tasty mixture then gets covered in roasted potatoes and cheese, which turns into a golden, cheesy topping after some time in the oven. Both little and big eaters will go wild for this baked delight!
